snippet: Syracuse’s Ryan Nassib threw for 246 yards and 3 touchdowns in his final home game, moving into second on the university’s career passing list, as the Orange gave No. 11 Louisville its first loss.
abstract: College Football East Roundup; Syracuse routs Louisville, 45-26; other scores noted.
